data.description: BRING ALL OFFERS, MOTIVATED SELLERS!  Do not miss this well maintained beautiful home. 5 bedrooms 3.5 bathrooms with the primary suite on the main level. This home backs to green space making the backyard a private oasis. The upstairs and the separate study/office downstairs ensures everyone has room to spread out and enjoy their hobbies. The first floor is all tile other than the primary suite, giving the home a spacious and cohesive feel. Both the front porch and back patio are covered adding to the outdoor spaces , making this home a must see. Siena is beautifully appointed master planned community, with 2 pools, splash pad, basketball and sand volley ball courts, walking trails , park space and community events.
